It should be noted this appears to be an Instagram hacking of the childs boyfriend, who the child has previously sent nude images to. On 9/6/2023 TFC Mueller attempted to contact the Child Victim in an attempt to gain more information, but was unsuccessful. A check through Maxmind shows the login IP address (173.73.123.138), after the sextortion occurred, is registered to Verizon Fios. On 9/6/2023 TFC Mueller authored a subpoena, for Verizon Fios subscriber information, and submitted it to the Howard County States Attorneys Office for endorsement. On 9/13/2023 TFC Mueller received the endorsed Verizon subpoena. TFC Mueller subsequently submitted the subpoena to Verizon. Case Open, investigation ongoing.

LIST OF EXHIBITS Verizon Subpoena Response NARRATIVE On 9/18/2023 TFC Mueller received the Verizon subpoena response. Verizon provided the following information: IP Address: 173.73.123.138 Start Time: 2023-07-20 12:42:07Z Stop Time: 2023-07-27 16:04:08Z Customer Name: Fumi Jibodu Account Address: 8603 ACCOKEEK STLAUREL, MD 207240000 Daytime Telephone 3013648553 Email Address: fumiyusuff_gold@yahoo.com Case Open, pending knock and talk

On 9/20/2023 TFC Mueller and Cpl. Heid responded to 8603 Accokeek Street Laurel, MD 20724 to conduct a knock and talk. Once on scene, Investigators were met with the Jibodu family who were very cooperative with the investigation. Knowing the mass majority of our suspects are males, TFC Mueller asked the family if any males currently reside within the residence. The family stated the only male residing at the residence is Muhammed Yusuff-Kareem (B/M DOB 6/4/2005). Muhammed came to talk with investigators and was explained the nature of the investigation. Muhammed stated he had no knowledge of the offense and consented to a search of his cell phone. No items of investigative interest were discovered. CASE CLOSED, BY EXCEPTION.
